'''Laser shears''' were high-tech gardening implements. After the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] infiltration software known as [[Systems Infiltration Manager|SIM]] took over computerized functions aboard the luxury star-cruiser ''[[Star of Empire]]'', gardening [[Droid/Legends|droids]] attempted to kill [[Zak Arranda/Legends|Zak]] and [[Tash Arranda/Legends|Tash Arranda]] and [[Dash Rendar/Legends|Dash Rendar]] with laser shears.

